result_object.geo_description: The lush jungles of Thailand promise adventure, while the serene beaches are the perfect place to splash in the sun. The Similan Islands feature some of the best dive sites in the world, where barracuda dart amid coral reefs and rock formations. Party in the nightclubs of Patong or linger over mango sticky rice at the famous Bangkok family restaurant Kao Neoo Korpanich. The city of Chiang Mai is an absolute must-visit; a mosaic of ancient temples, massage parlors, music venues, and markets.

place.description: Welcome to Big Boys' Burger Club - Patong Beach, a culinary destination just moments away from Patong Beach and Bangla Road. Indulge in a range of thoughtfully crafted artisan burgers, each designed to offer a distinct taste experience: - Our beef burgers feature 200g of quality grass-fed Australian beef, skillfully dry-aged, double-grounded, and charbroiled to perfection. - For chicken enthusiasts, our buttermilk marinated chicken breast brings tenderness and juiciness to every bite. - Delight in the comfort of our slow-cooked Carolina-style pork shoulder burger. - Our barramundi fillet fish burger offers a delightful combination of flavors and textures. - The vegan option presents a Beyond Meat patty, a plant-based delight that mirrors the taste of beef. Complementing our burger selection are our signature homemade sauces, daily baked buns, and sides like our tempting loaded fries. Our inviting ambiance is crafted with cosy furniture, offering a comfortable space to savor your meal.
place.name: Big Boys' Burger Club - Patong Beach
